The term '''seelie fey''' was used to generically refer to any [[fey]] who was [[good]] or otherwise generally honorable in their dealings with mortals. It could also refer to:

*Any fey member of the [[Summer Court]], or
*[[Seelie]], a species of fey found in the Yuirwood.
{{Disambig}}
